Title: Improved handling of baking errors in Agent Bakery
Level: 1
Edition: cee
Component: agents
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
State: unknown
Version: 1.2.7i3
Date: 1435913565
Targetversion: future

When baking of one agent failed for any reason, the following agents were
not baked anymore. This has been changed now. The error message is printed
out to the user and the bakery continues to build the other agents.

Improved handling of unbacked agents for hosts.
